":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和平散去 之後俾你開槍掃射 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"ebeef38bd564441b44211ad5b062a6439a04a70e","tid":1733968,"uid":138736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"而家班賤種捉晒啲醫療手足<br />\npoly 入面物資開始短缺<br />\n賤種繼續圍城<br />\n就係想要手足投降<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7點，香港人幫拖</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cc8178afbc537f1fcb9c81b4fbd594e1c0485b04","tid":1733968,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"一出嚟就開槍 然後叫你說嚟俾佢當耙咁射"},{"pid":"6da16192060f76da13365a33f173728404a376d0","tid":1733968,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"散你老母咩，一出現就係咁放催淚彈，<br />\n又射胡椒彈，散落地底咩，<br />\n痴撚線，班狗迫到有人睇唔開係橋到跳落嚟，全港暴動都似..."},{"pid":"76702ad314981519df233a74137a84369ab9dc42","tid":1733968,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"黑警講野都信?"},{"pid":"e52243b37628f4948f2968d5d5ac856471a90662","tid":1733968,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"中大已經知佢地信唔過"},{"pid":"4ef54c711bddd97436ea80d9fa80a95d1ce1e099","tid":1733968,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"推，大家要升level，我地人多要把握呢個優勢，多啲上街幫手，唔洗驚黑警毅進狗，佢地成班讀唔成書廢柴社會最低層賤種，聲大大無料到，只識濫捕告唔入，死死地氣放返出黎，打狗放火食警嫂無後果吹我地唔脹，照樣生勾勾照上街抗爭屌狗做野<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母黑警毅進狗死全家，落地獄"},{"pid":"b64ec8bb5c9c967ecbff42ae306296f643eba3d7","tid":1733968,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"班狗好明顯架硬屈搞事然後圍理大，然件事合理化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}